{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4040","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"樂善國小通學步道經費核定通過","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4040-1.jpeg","sequence":4037,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.1 加速宜居城市建設","link":"https://www.facebook.com/groups/a7xinlinkou/permalink/701684721936779/","author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-04-16T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"樂善國小通學步道經費核定通過"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小通學步道經費核定通過"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小前方有一塊私人地，感謝里長、校長及地主的協助，讓樂善國小前方可以做完整的通學步道以及規劃接送區避車彎。這部分近期可以先行施工。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另外，原市府規劃的方案（如圖）未將樂學路上的擋土牆納入，但雅倫認為舊有擋土牆及圍牆年久失修，我建議一併規劃打除，以現今的工法重做安全合適的圍牆，也讓出人行空間。並建議通學步道要串連到樂善社區，讓樂善國小及文德非營利幼兒園的孩子都可以安全上學！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-1.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感謝雅倫！！ 期望現在難看的人行道能有更好的利用及成為接送兒童的安全區域！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-3.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫爭取的樂善國小全區通學步道改善 如圖，目前也已送前瞻計畫，希望儘快核定儘快施作！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-4.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-4.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-5.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-5.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"_20240809-樂善國小周邊通學步道準備開工"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2024/08/09 樂善國小周邊通學步道準備開工！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下禮拜一工班正式進場，雅倫今日特別與各局處走訪兩校，做施工前的說明會～\n開學在即，希望趁暑假期間加緊腳步，施工期間也必須預留行人通道，降低對學生開學後的影響！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-6.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-6.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"樂善國小通學步道經費核定通過","depth":2,"text":"樂善國小通學步道經費核定通過"},{"id":"_20240809-樂善國小周邊通學步道準備開工","depth":2,"text":"2024/08/09 樂善國小周邊通學步道準備開工！"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s4040.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s4040.md","_extension":"md"}